{"id":22660412878,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAFRqp1zg","head_branch":"DHIS2-20991","head_sha":"a09a927c088d015fdd15469c727b05672df77ad5","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":47600,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: change default order to created desc and add supporting indices DHIS2-20991","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":59288114901,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAANzdjW1Q","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878","pull_requests":[{"id":3334626934,"number":23093,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/23093","head":{"ref":"DHIS2-20991","sha":"a09a927c088d015fdd15469c727b05672df77ad5","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"abebed255000af4985ccdea9e307d195171a3ac0","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-03-04T08:02:03Z","updated_at":"2026-03-04T08:15:36Z","run_started_at":"2026-03-04T08:02:03Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/59288114901","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/22660412878/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: fix trackerevent join regressions in TE store DHIS2-20991\n\nTwo regressions introduced by the programid denormalization:\n\n1. eventStatus=SCHEDULE/OVERDUE and assignedUserMode=ANY/PROVIDED regressed\n   from sub-ms to ~900ms and ~92ms respectively. Both paths joined trackerevent\n   with only ev.enrollmentid = en.enrollmentid. The new programid-prefixed\n   indices (in_trackerevent_program_occurreddate, in_trackerevent_program_assigneduser)\n   require ev.programid in the predicate to be usable. Fix: add\n   ev.programid = en.programid to both join paths.\n\n2. order=enrolledAt combined with filters regressed from 11-17s to 17-26s.\n   addSubquerySelect unconditionally added te.created to the inner SELECT. On\n   the enrolledAt path the outer ORDER BY uses en_enrollmentdate, not te.created,\n   so the column was unused but grew the sort row width past work_mem, causing\n   80MB+ disk sorts per parallel worker. Fix: omit te.created on the enrolledAt\n   path, using a LinkedHashSet to collect SELECT columns so an explicit\n   order=createdAt still deduplicates naturally.\n\nResults after fix (EXPLAIN ANALYZE, warmup=4, Sierra Leone 9M TE DB):\n  eventStatus=SCHEDULE:    908ms -\u003e 0.3ms\n  eventStatus=OVERDUE:     919ms -\u003e 0.2ms\n  assignedUserMode=ANY:     92ms -\u003e 0.1ms\n  assignedUserMode=PROVIDED: 93ms -\u003e 0.2ms\n  enrolledAt+enrollmentStatus: 17,209ms -\u003e 8,255ms (below master 11,406ms)\n  enrolledAt+eventStatus:  26,241ms -\u003e 16,044ms (below master 17,352ms)\n  enrolledAt+filterAttr:    7,070ms -\u003e  3,045ms (below master  4,023ms)","author":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"a09a927c088d015fdd15469c727b05672df77ad5","tree_id":"e39fe8c77b29482a59efa36c6b75ead3e729e02e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:01:40Z","committer":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/108998